channel.title: 2 question on jar files and cache files
channel.description: i know i should be on tutorials, but i cant find one, i guess i have no brain lol, i should know this sht, im not new to server making, anyway 1 is for some reason i fail at making jar files and cache files, i think my jar is fine, it think its really my cache, i jared and signed my client.class, or what ever file it is, my cache, how do i set that up? do i just copy all the files in spirites into a file and zip it? or all the files in cache? im so confused? thanks

item.title: 2 question on jar files and cache files
item.dc:creator: @Get_Blitz Get Blitz
item.description:
@Get_Blitz wrote:

First of all you do not only jar your client class, you jar the whole client folder except the sprites. for the cache you open the main cache folder and zip everything inside it.
